# WallDraw MicroPython Turtle

# Features
- Based on Hackaday project: https://hackaday.io/project/193338-minimal-pico-vertical-plotter
- As in the original project
    - Uses 28BYJ-48 stepper motors to control drawing gondola up and down.
    - Uses SG90 servo to control pen up/down.
    - Power supply for both Pico and the motors are from PC USB port.
- This project is written in MicroPython, while the original project was written in Arduino, and our drawing is done using the turtle graphics library like functions. 

